description:
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;Southern Health NHS Foundation Trust are recruiting for passionate, ambitious and committed Mental Health Nurses that are newly qualified or are due to qualify in 2021. Our bespoke preceptorship program will support you to kick-start your career and allow you to be confident in what you love doing.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We are looking for Mental Health Nurses to join our Acute and Psychiatric Intensive Care wards Parklands Hospital. Both wards are busy settings with ample opportunities for learning and expanding your clinical skills as you take this next exciting step in your career. You will be joining a welcoming team that is committed to providing high quality, person-centered care.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;As a newly qualified nurse you will be offered tailored support and will have the opportunity to learn from clinically focused leaders. Your professional development is our priority and there is a wide range of training available to inform and enhance your clinical practice.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;About the location&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Parklands Hospital is located in Basingstoke, close to rail and bus links with free parking on site. The unit is beautifully situated next to leafy green spaces, and we benefit from an on-site nursery on the adjacent Basingstoke and North Hampshire Hospital site.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Why Southern Health? What we will offer you…&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;£24,907 to £30,615 pa based on full time hours&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;12 month preceptorship program&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Support with clinical skills and mandatory training, annual performance reviews and development reviews&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Generous annual leave allowance, starting at 27 days + bank holidays&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Continuing CPD development through our extensive trust education and training programmes&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Free DBS and paid Update Service&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Company Pension Scheme&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Discount Card&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Free parking on site&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;If you have any questions or would like to visit us please contact Charlotte Kirk 01256 376373 or at charlotte.kirk@southernhealth.nhs.uk&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
